        <content type="html" xml:base="https://blog.jimmac.eu/posts/pixel-inktober-2022/">&lt;p&gt;Just like &lt;a href=&quot;&#x2F;posts&#x2F;pixel-inktober&#x2F;&quot;&gt;last year&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;, October was filled with quick pixel dailies. I decided to only post &lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;mastodon.social&#x2F;@jimmac&quot;&gt;on mastodon&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;, but due to the twitter exodus couldn&#x27;t quite post the 30kB images for the two remaining days. Good old blog post it is!&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
